a的人进行了交谈。在三种情况下，原告能够恢复对至少一个丢失的帐户的访问权限，但最终都引起了Meta法律团队的关注。</p><p>该公司认为，根据其服务条款，其损害赔偿金不超过100美元。但是，一些原告获得了数千美元的奖励 - 与那些企业围绕其Fa​​cebook或Instagram在场的人的收入损失相比，这些原告仍然可能苍白。我们绘制了这些用户和Meta逻辑的混合结果，以给予他们如此多的关注。</p><p> - 马特·史密斯（Mat Smith）</p><h3 id="jump-link-the-biggest-stories-you-might-have-missed">您可能错过的最大故事</h3><h3 id="jump-link-"></h3><p><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ssds-140014262.html">2024年最好的SSD</a></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-reportedly-has-plans-for-a-thinner-iphone-macbook-pro-and-apple-watch-171137550.html">据报道，苹果计划有更薄的iPhone，MacBook Pro和Apple Watch的计划</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/more-than-1000-students-pledge-not-to-work-at-google-and-amazon-due-to-project-nimbus-042439081.html">由于 Nimbus 项目，超过 1000 名学生承诺不再在谷歌和亚马逊工作</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-house-will-open-two-locations-in-texas-and-pennsylvania-in-2025-213033751.html">Netflix House将于2025年在德克萨斯州和宾夕法尼亚州开设两个地点</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-webb-telescopes-dazzling-nebula-image-supports-a-long-held-theory-210229206.html">韦伯望远镜令人眼花the乱的星云图像支持了一个长期以来的理论</a></p><p><em>您可以将这些报告直接直接发送到收件箱。</em><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/about/newsletter/"><em>在这里订阅！</em></a></p><p></p><h2 id="jump-link-amazon-says-its-cut-down-on-its-plastic-air-pillows"> <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-says-its-cut-down-on-those-plastic-air-pillows-in-packages-222953642.html">Amazon says it&#39;s cut down on its plastic air pillows</a></h2><h3 id="jump-link-popping-them-makes-me-jump"> Popping them makes me jump.</h3><h3 id="jump-link-"></h3><p> You may have already noticed, but Amazon says it&#39;s reduced its use of plastic airbags included with its packages, shifting to compostable paper filler in most cases.它计划在今年年底之前消除使用它们。 It&#39;s a move in the right direction: In 2021, the nonprofit ocean conservation group Oceana estimated that the waste produced from plastic air pillows alone “would circle the Earth more than 600 times.”</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-says-its-cut-down-on-those-plastic-air-pillows-in-packages-222953642.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><p></p><h2 id="jump-link-a-remastered-beyond-good-and-evil-arrives-next-week"> <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-beyond-good-and-evil-remaster-will-be-released-next-week-for-real-230001749.html">A remastered Beyond Good and Evil arrives next week</a></h2><h3 id="jump-link-but-wheres-that-sequel"> But where&#39;s that sequel?</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/the-beyond-good-and-evil-remaster-will-be-released-next-week-for-real-230001749.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-06/e1de1060-2fa9-11ef-b5cb-154b15c9ca4a" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-06/e1de1060-2fa9-11ef-b5cb-154b15c9ca4a" style="height:380px;width:675px;" alt="TMA" data-uuid="52e7e38e-c9a3-371d-a8bb-de2466af048c"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">育碧</div></figure></a><p>Ubisoft has released a trailer for its remake of the cult classic game Beyond Good and Evil, adding that it will launch on June 25. The understated cult hit has been upgraded to 4K and 60FPS – it was initially released on the PS2, so you&#39;ll see the difference.它将在PC，PlayStation 5，PlayStation 4，Nintendo Switch，Xbox One和Xbox系列X/S上提供，并在下个月发售物理副本。 What about the sequel that has been <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2008-05-28-beyond-good-and-evil-2-revealed-at-ubidays-2008.html">revealed</a> , teased,<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2016-01-30-beyond-good-and-evil-2.html">promised</a> , and… <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-06-14-beyond-good-evil-2-gameplay-demo-e3.html">seen</a> (by me!)?无话可说。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-beyond-good-and-evil-remaster-will-be-released-next-week-for-real-230001749.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a> </p><p></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2 id="jump-link-the-us-will-ban-sales-of-kaspersky-antivirus-software"> <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-us-will-ban-sales-of-kaspersky-antivirus-software-next-month-205106837.html">The US will ban sales of Kaspersky antivirus software</a></h2><h3 id="jump-link-after-years-of-scrutiny-over-the-russian-companys-government-ties"> After years of scrutiny over the Russian company&#39;s government ties.</h3><h3 id="jump-link-"></h3><p> The Biden administration has taken sweeping action to ban Kaspersky Labs from selling its antivirus products to US customers.消息人士告诉<em>路透社</em>，该公司与俄罗斯政府的联系使其成为安全风险。卡巴斯基在报告中包含的一份声明中补充说，其活动并没有威胁到国家安全，并且会采取法律选择。 FCC将卡巴斯基（Kaspersky）列入其在2022年构成不可接受的安全风险的公司名单，而早在2017年，美国的联邦机构禁止了卡巴斯基产品。 The company cannot sell to new customers starting in July.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-us-will-ban-sales-of-kaspersky-antivirus-software-next-month-205106837.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-how-small-claims-court-became-metas-customer-service-hotline-111555251.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-how-small-claims-court-became-metas-customer-service-hotline-111555251.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> eb8dcd5e-9fbb-429c-842a-9e87647b01b7 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mat Smith]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 21 Jun 2024 11:15:55 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1718959570</ingested><modified> 2024-06-21T08:46:18+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mat Smith]]></category><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Ffb30dd40-9049-11ee-adf7-b6b290e5feac&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=07f43bfdd92aed27d25c596756ac795f08ea950f" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Ffb30dd40-9049-11ee-adf7-b6b290e5feac&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=04c262b67b7f5704629210cd61048ec23593ac01" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[FILE - Attendees visit the Meta booth at the Game Developers Conference 2023 in San Francisco on March 22, 2023. Facebook parent Meta Platforms deliberately engineered its social platforms to hook kids and knew — but never disclosed — that it had received millions of complaints about underage users on Instagram but only disabled a fraction of those accounts, according to a newly unsealed legal complaint described in reports from the Wall Street Journal and the New York Times. (AP Photo/Jeff Chiu, File)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Meta Risks to Kids Unredacted Document]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best smart displays for 2024]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>自 2017 年亚马逊首款 Echo Show 首次亮相以来，智能显示器已经取得了长足的发展。事实上，直到大约一年后谷歌推出自己的硬件产品线加入竞争，该类别才真正形成自己的特色。现在，这两家公司基本上主导了智能显示领域，每家公司都提供了自己的带有屏幕的智能助手。<br><br>正是这种屏幕使智能显示器比<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smart-speakers-151515264.html">智能扬声器</a>更加有用。例如，您不仅可以让语音助手背诵当前的天气预报，还可以查看五天的天气预报。当您询问购物清单或日历时，情况也是如此。只需一目了然即可轻松阅读整个列表或当天的约会。此外，触摸屏还提供扬声器无法提供的其他好处，例如观看视频或检查网络摄像头以了解谁在您的前门。多年来，我们测试并使用了许多智能显示器，下面是我们为您挑选的当今最佳智能显示器的首选列表。</p><h2 id="jump-link-best-smart-displays-for-2024"> 2024 年最佳智能显示器</h2><p><core-commerce id="196a31693b23403982f928e1b97f4f17" data-type="product-list"></p><p><core-commerce id="6881dd19ce3145e8af6d337617b80bd4" data-type="product-list"></p><p><core-commerce id="26455cb90e284708b12b282d672c8c94" data-type="product-list"></p><p><core-commerce id="9608eb95a32f49bb813b90a49cbf7ec3" data-type="product-list"></p><p><core-commerce id="3205a3de0f8141d792b5c7604e2d1adc" data-type="product-list"></p><h2 id="jump-link-what-to-consider-before-buying-a-smart-display">购买智能显示器之前要考虑什么</h2><h3 id="jump-link-amazon-vs-google-voice-assistants">亚马逊与谷歌语音助手</h3><p>在寻找最适合您的智能显示器时，您应该问的第一个问题是您更喜欢亚马逊还是谷歌的生态系统。如果你家里有很多谷歌智能设备，比如 Nest 恒温器和安全摄像头，或者即使你使用谷歌 Pixel 智能手机作为日常司机，那么谷歌驱动的型号可能更有意义。如果您有亚马逊产品，例如 Fire TV Stick 或 Ring cam，从兼容性的角度来看，亚马逊显然是更好的选择。当然，在同一个家庭中拥有竞争对手公司的产品是完全可以接受的，但要意识到它们可能从一开始就无法无缝地协同工作。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>除此之外，这两个系统还提供一些独特的功能。例如，如果您拥有现有的 Google 帐户并使用日历和照片等服务，那么 Google 的效果最佳。我们特别喜欢谷歌智能显示屏，因为它们可以很好地用作数码相框。你可以将其设置为自动从 Google 照片库中提取朋友和家人的照片，并且该算法足够智能，可以使用它认为最好的照片 - 因此，模糊照片或半闭眼睛图像的可能性较小例如，出现。不过，虽然你可以使用亚马逊的显示器作为数码相框，但这个过程并不像谷歌那么直观，而且亚马逊没有任何可以与谷歌相媲美的照片分类算法。</p><p>这似乎是一个小问题，但考虑到显示屏 90% 的时间都处于待机状态，它作为数码相框的第二功能非常受欢迎。所有 Google 智能显示屏还支持 YouTube 和 YouTube TV、分步烹饪说明以及 Google Assistant 的所有常见功能，例如天气预报。与手机上的助手一样，它也具有语音识别功能，因此只有您可以看到您的日历约会，而其他人则看不到。</p><p>另一方面，亚马逊的智能显示器略有不同。他们提供了一些替代的视频流媒体选项，包括 Amazon Prime、NBC 和 Hulu，而不是 YouTube。它们还配备了两个浏览器（Silk 和 Firefox），您可以使用它们来搜索网络或观看 YouTube 视频——鉴于缺乏专用应用程序，这是一个足够方便的解决方法。由于与 SideChef 和 A​​llRecipes 等来源的合作，亚马逊设备还提供分步烹饪说明。烹饪说明有时还包括短片。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/best-smart-display-202448797.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-smart-display-202448797.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> bc3b9f48-dfe2-36bb-9aeb-d31abeb9f6e7 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Nicole Lee,Valentina Palladino]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 21 Jun 2024 09:01:26 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1718960488</ingested><modified> 2024-06-21T09:01:44+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[amazon]]></category><category><![CDATA[BuyersGuide]]></category><category><![CDATA[smarthome2020]]></category><category><![CDATA[thebuyersguide]]></category><category><![CDATA[google]]></category><category><![CDATA[commerce]]></category><category><![CDATA[lenovo]]></category><category><![CDATA[gear]]></category><category><![CDATA[home]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Nicole Lee]]></category><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-06%2Fb80e08e0-24db-11ef-bfa7-26c9986e422c&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=b5679d4ffd93efd7edd9f40faed0e2a0e27eaeba" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><!