ion:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div></div><p>今天关于 X 的讨论让人回想起<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/beyond-good--evil-is-getting-a-20th-anniversary-edition-in-early-2024-183535329.html"><ins>世界最初是如何了解</ins></a>计划中的重制版的。它的列表出现在 Xbox Store 上，由于技术故障，2023 年育碧 Plus 上曾短暂出现过一个不完整的版本。此外，每当《超越善恶》出现时，普通读者可能会发现自己对这部十多年来一直被<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2008-05-28-beyond-good-and-evil-2-revealed-at-ubidays-2008.html"><ins>揭露</ins></a>、 <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2017-06-14-beyond-good-and-evil-2-interview-e3-2017.html"><ins>嘲笑</ins></a>、 <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2016-01-30-beyond-good-and-evil-2.html"><ins>承诺</ins></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-06-14-beyond-good-evil-2-gameplay-demo-e3.html"><ins>观看的</ins></a>续集感到好奇。不，此更新似乎没有带来有关该项目的任何新信息。</p><p>这是一个多么漫长、奇怪的开发周期。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-beyond-good-and-evil-remaster-will-be-released-next-week-for-real-230001749.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-beyond-good-and-evil-remaster-will-be-released-next-week-for-real-230001749.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f35b60cb-d876-4911-ae15-4a22cb3ad04e</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Anna Washenko]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 20 Jun 2024 23:00:01 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1718922970</ingested><modified> 2024-06-20T22:36:15+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Game Consoles]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Anna Washenko]]></category><medi